name: Axie Infinity
public_notice: Axie Infinity team is looking for early testers for the launch of their new game, Atia's Legacy, an Axie based MMO. Pre-register at https://axieinfinity.com/pre-register/?ref=2imuudnf

description.en: AXS is the governance token for the Axie Infinity game. Token holders will be able to shape and vote for the direction of the game universe. This is unlike traditional games where all decisions are made by the game developers. AXS holders will be able to stake their tokens to earn more AXS and evenÂ vote for governance proposals.
